{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_03_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 僕まで恥ずかしくなってきた",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタイン当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Valentine's Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、リズノワは準備出来たか？\n三十分後には会場入りだから、忘れ物がないように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ is LizNoir ready?\nYou will be at the venue in 30 minutes‚ so don't forget anything ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……おっと、まだ取り込み中か）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…… oops‚ they are still preparing.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、これは月ストとサニピのみんなのチョコ\nトリエルは……今いないからテーブルに置いておくか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ok‚ those are chocolates for everyone on the Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace.\nTRINITYAiLE is not here…… right now‚ so let's put them on the table.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央にははい、これ\n去年より美味しくなってるはずだから、期待していいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For Rio‚ here.\nIt should taste better than last year‚ so you can count on it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それから、こころには焼きプリンと……\n愛には、カロリー控えめの豆腐ガトーショコラね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ for Kokoro‚ baked pudding and ……\nFor Ai‚ a low-calorie tofu gateau chocolat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（みんな凄く喜んでるみたいだな）\n（葵も頑張った甲斐があったというものだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Everyone must be very happy about it.)\n（It was worth Aoi's effort.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワは、イベントが終わってから食べようか\n怖いマネージャーが睨んでるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe LizNoir will eat after the event is over.\nBecause there is a scary manager staring always.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "聞こえてるぞ。ひょっとして俺のことか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can hear you. Are you talking about me by any chance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "聞こえるように言ったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said it so you could hear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……ほら\nおやつは後にしてそろそろ会場に行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ ……‚ look‚\nsnacks later‚ it's time to go to the venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（……さすがリズノワ、リハーサルでも迫力満点だな）\n（あれなら、本番でも問題ないだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…… indeed‚ LizNoir‚ you're so powerful‚ even in rehearsal.)\n(That one should be fine for the show.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.333333300004,
          "startTime": 70
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "やぁ、お疲れ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ葵……あれ、リハーサルは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's up Aoi …… Hey‚ what's with the rehearsal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "フットライトの調節するから、僕達は少し休憩だって\n莉央達は袖で休んでるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said we'll take a break while they adjust the footlights.\nRio and the others are resting at the side of the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、難しい顔して\n考えごとしてたみたいだけど、今のリハのこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ You look so serioius.\nIt is just like there is a problem. The rehearsal we just had?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。本番に向けて\nまだまだ、いくらでも考えることがあるからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh. For the show.\nThere's still plenty to think about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……真剣なんだ……\nやっぱり凄いね、ちゃんと見てくれてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm …… you're serious ……\nAwesome tho‚ you're caring about us seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "何か言ったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did you say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nah~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……？　そういえばさっきはみんな喜んでくれた\nみたいじゃないか。頑張った甲斐があったな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay……? Oh‚ by the way‚ it looks like everyone\nwas happy with the chocolates earlier. It was worth the effort!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね\nでもあれ、実際にやってみたら結構大変だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ well.\nBut that was actually pretty hard to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "お菓子作りは好きだけど、あれだけ沢山作るのは\nたまに……一年に一回くらいでいいや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like to make sweets‚ but I can't make that many.\nSometimes …… just once a year or so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "……それより、これを持ってきたんだ\nまぁ、{user}君の分のチョコなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… but more importantly‚ I brought you this.\nWell‚ it's chocolate for you‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "俺にも作ってくれたのか、ありがとう。でも、なんで\n今なんだ？　事務所で渡してくれれば良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You made it for me‚ thanks. But why now?\nYou should have given it to me at the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "いつ渡そうかと考えてたら\nここまで持って来ちゃったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was trying to figure out when to give it to you‚\nand I brought it here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、人前でむやみに男の人にプレゼントを\n渡すなって、前にそう言ったのは、そっちじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're the one who told me not to give gifts to men\nin public in the first place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
